  "label": "Mavren Cothel",
  "description": "This individual is an undead remnant shaped by prolonged entombment, with light skin stretched tight over sharply articulated bone structure. Gray eyes sit deep in hollowed sockets, and white hair hangs in an unkempt fall that exposes a gaunt scalp and pronounced cranial ridges. The mouthline is collapsed and tooth-bared, and the hands are long-fingered with rigid, desiccated joints that limit fine motion. Their frame is lean to the point of skeletal definition, preserving a cavern-born stillness that favors sudden, economical bursts of violence.",
